These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, strawberry
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, bike
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person eating zucchini is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | zucchini   | strawberry   |
| Transport   | bike | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, milk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
2. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | milk | water   |
| Sport      | tennis | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: potato, lettuce
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, ambient
1. the person eating potato is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
2. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | lettuce | potato |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | ambient     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, watermelon
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony
1. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the person eating avocado##8
2. the person eating avocado is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Food   | watermelon | avocado |
| Pet    | goldfish    | pony |

 #################################

 
